    "featureType": "projectfu.supportModule",
    "data": {
      "description": "<p><strong>Counts as two enabled modules.</strong></p><hr /><p>This personal vehicle can fly, and its <strong>distance</strong> becomes ×3.</p><p>While you are driving this <strong>personal vehicle</strong>, your <strong>melee</strong> attacks can target <strong>flying </strong>creatures, and none of the creatures inside the <strong>personal vehicle</strong> can be targeted by <strong>melee</strong> attacks unless the attacker is flying or is somehow able to reach flying targets.</p><p>These benefits do not apply while the <strong>personal vehicle</strong> is inactive or grounded, while you are in <strong>Crisis</strong>, or while you are <strong>covering</strong> another creature with the <strong>Guard</strong> action. Additionally, if a creature aboard this <strong>personal vehicle</strong> suffers <strong>air,</strong> <strong>bolt</strong> or <strong>ice</strong> damage during a conflict, the benefits of this module cease until the start of your next turn.</p>",
      "complex": true
    },
    "source": "FUTF168",
    "fuid": "aerial-module"
  },
